    <h1 id="risk">Risks & Causes of Hypertension</h1>

    <h5><img src="images/aging.png" alt=""> Aging</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/genetic.png" alt=""> Genetics (family history)</h5>
    <h5> <img src="images/Medications.png" alt=""> Side effects of certain medications (such as: Advil)</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/diabetes.png" alt=""> Diabetes</h5>
    <h5> <img src="images/food.png" alt=""> Unhealthy Diet</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/sedentary.png" alt=""> Physical Inactivity</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/smoking.png" alt=""> Excessive use of Tobacco & Alcohol</h5>

    <h1 id="complic">Complications of Untreated Hypertension</h1>
    <h5><img src="images/MI.png" alt=""> Miocardial Infarction (Heart Ischemia)</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/stroke.png" alt=""> Stroke (Brain Ischemia)</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/kidney.png" alt=""> Chronic Kidney Disease (Dialysis)</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/Glaucoma.png" alt=""> Eye damage (Glaucoma)</h5>

    <h1 id="sympt">Common Symptoms of Hypertension</h1>
    <h5><img src="images/danger.png" alt=""> No symptoms (known as the Silent Killer)</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/Headache.png" alt=""> Headache</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/blurry.png" alt=""> Blurry vision</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/nosebleeds.png" alt=""> Nose Bleeds</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/buzz.png" alt=""> Buzzing in the ear</h5>


    <h1 id="prevent">Hypertension Prevention</h1>
    <h5><img src="images/hdiet.png" alt=""> Diet (Low salt, Low fat)</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/phactive.png" alt=""> Regular Physical Activity</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/nosmoke.png" alt=""> Reduce Tobacco (see Tobacco cessation) and Alcohol Consumption</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/MedicalExams.png" alt=""> Regular Medical Exams (for early diagnosis)</h5>


    <h1 id="manag">Hypertension Management</h1>
    <h5><img src="images/blpressure.png" alt=""> Regularly checking blood pressure</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/Medpressure.png" alt=""> Seek hypertension treatment (with Prescribed Medication)</h5>
    <h5><img src="images/Lowsalt.png" alt=""> Follow a strict diet, Low salt (No added salt if possible) & Low fat</h5>

